-- Hindalco Gains in Mumbai on Report of Bid for Rio Tinto Alcan's Division
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-06-21T03:35:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/hindalco-gains-in-mumbai-on-report-of-bid-for-rio-tinto-alcan-s-division.html

          
          
             Hindalco Industries Ltd. gained as
much as 3.9 percent in Mumbai trading after the Economic Times
newspaper reported, citing people it didn’t name, that the
company’s unit Novelis Inc. may bid for the rolled products
division of Rio Tinto Alcan.  
          
          


  


        